Package de.dfki.oms.webapp.handler.impl

Implementations of classes to dispatch and handle HTTP requests to the OMS.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddBlockHandler
    Handler for adding blocks to an OMM.
    AddHandler
    Handler for adding data an OMM or its blocks.
    BlockFormatHandler
    A handler to retrieve a requested block and respond its format as a MIME type.
    BlockHandler
    Handler that retrieves a block by its ID given in the request and responds it in form of an HTML table.
    ContributorEntityTypeHandler
    Handler that retrieves and responds a list of all known OMM entity types.
    DesMultiLangHandler
    Handler that responds a list of all languages for which the block does not have a description yet.
    EditHandler
    Handler that edits an OMM element (from header to block field).
    EmptyBlockHandler
    Handler that responds a block without payload.
    EmptyHeaderHandler
    Handler that responds an empty header.
    HeaderHandler
    Handler that responds a header as an HTML table.
    MineTypeHandler
    Handler that responds all known MIME types used for OMMFormats.
    OMMTypeHandler
    Handler that responds all known types used for block payloads.
    PayloadIdInfoKeysHandler
    Handler that responds all known payload ID info keys.
    PayloadRelationHandler
    Handler that responds a list of structure relations.
    PayloadTypeHandler
    Handler that responds "OMM Indentification Information".
    RemoveHandler
    Handler that removes an OMM element using a given path.
    SubjectTypeHandler
    Handler that responds a list of all known subject types.
    SubjectValueHandler
    Handler that responds a block's complete subject.
    TitleMultiLangHandler
    Handler that responds a list of all languages for which the block does not have a title yet.
    UpdateHandler
    Handler that responds a block's payload as an HTML table.
